description:
Wondering what weapons to use for your party? With the Weapon Pack, you can equip your favorite Goddesses with awesome weapons! Each character also receives two new weapons!

The Weapon Pack includes:
- Neptune's Weapon Set
- Noire's Weapon Set
- Blanc's Weapon Set
- Vert's Weapon Set
- Nepgear's Weapon Set
- Uni's Weapon Set
- Rom's Weapon Set
- Ram's Weapon Set
- Uzume's Weapon Set
- Older Neptune's Weapon Set
- IF's Weapon Set
- Compa's Weapon Set
- B-Sha's Weapon Set
- S-Sha's Weapon Set
- C-Sha's Weapon Set
- K-Sha's Weapon Set
name: Weapon Pack
